<title>USA: FULL TEXT - MCI Statement.</title>
<headline>FULL TEXT - MCI Statement.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1996-11-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>MCI Communications Corp said it is talks on a possible &quot;strategic&quot; merger with British Telecommunications Plc, confirming market speculation about a deal.</p>
<p>Following is a full text of its press release.</p>
<p>------------PRESS RELEASE---------------------</p>
<p>WASHINGTON, Nov. 1 /PRNewswire/ -- MCI announced this afternoon that its board of directors is considering a possible strategic merger with BT.  MCI anticipates that its deliberations will be concluded this weekend and an announcement will be made prior to Monday morning.  MCI also said that there can be no assurances that an agreement will be entered into or that any transaction will be consummated.</p>
</text>
